Package: AnnotateIt
Type: Package
Title: AnnotateIt: a simple and user-friendly R package designed to streamline the process of text data annotation for classification tasks
Version: 0.1
Date: 2023-12-07
Author: Gabriel Cantharino Granjo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Gabriel Cantharino Granjo <gabriel.granjo@fgv.br>
Description: AnnotateIt is a simple and user-friendly R package designed to streamline the process of text data annotation for classification tasks. This package leverages the power of Shiny, a web application framework for R, to create an interactive annotation environment, ideal for projects that require accurate human-labeled text data for training machine learning models. The package is also helpful in boosting the productivity of small groups in annotation tasks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Imports:
  shiny,
  shinythemes,
  htmltools
